Log4Tango is a light and custom version of log4tango for Tango.
See doc/html/index.html for details.

The log4tango library port from the LOG4J Java library was 
initiated by Bastiaan Bakker <bastiaan.bakker@lifeline.nl>.

Log for C++ (short name: log4tango), a C++ library for flexible logging.
